Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡分別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 櫻滿集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你盡讓人操心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛空？整個區全部嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:28.20,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(474,665)}void
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六本木要塞是由一顆少女的心構成的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻滿真名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好的和虛空相關的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:43.79,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(622,665)}void
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這之後就要另外收費了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷漠的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一如既往的遲鈍啊 集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:02.96,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}再生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於出現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Da'at：生命樹中隱藏的質點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知識的守墓者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.35,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,665)}Da'at
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守墓者？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修一郎已經很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們也從旁協助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追 集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙想要犧牲祈來復活真名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把祈帶到哪兒去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻滿集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你無論如何都要跟來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就全都回想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你親自封印的有關真名的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集 已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜開眼睛 集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好漂亮啊 真名姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？這是姐姐的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只告訴集一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 聽得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫集 櫻滿集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是櫻滿真名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問你名字呢 名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特萊登
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是從海裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}特萊登：取自手塚治虫的海王子/小飛龍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就叫做特萊登
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 在那天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:06:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和姐姐真名遇到了一個少年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名叫那個少年特萊登 也就是涯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我們共同度過了一個夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落的耶誕節那年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家笑著度過的最後一個夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 真的要跳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題啦 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到你了 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 不是跳過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 在一起度過的那段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對我而言 成了最親密的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我最喜歡的溫柔的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我最好的朋友涯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我人生中最快樂最幸福的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了涯 也忘了真名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.59,0:07:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把祈還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個少女原本就是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了與真名意識相通而創造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接用臨時實驗體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸還這個詞語還真是不恰當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造出來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 真名是最先觸摸到了始祖之石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啟病毒的第一個感染者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了肉體的她的靈魂被注入了新的身體裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們之手 即將再次降臨到世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的復活也就是失落的耶誕節的再次到來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啟病毒會在世界範圍肆虐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須成為其見證人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知識對你好像有什麼期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:29.05,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(455,665)}Da'at
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來 你只是個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上嘴在那裡看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能妨礙他喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 他將通過祈向真名求婚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她所選擇的伴侶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將成為下一代的新人類的始祖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是任性的夏娃只要有石頭也能夠控制住她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請你對兩人的未來獻上祝福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 我和別人結婚的話 你會寂寞嗎 集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是特萊登
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特萊登? 不行的 那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的 集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會和特萊登結婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 用和大人一樣的目光看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用淫蕩的目光  好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:10:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 集用大人的眼光看我也可以喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你 集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是病毒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個斑點是那個石頭的病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親告訴我的 那會使人瘋狂的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名想把集怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓已經死掉的你復活的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你是我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:11:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以隨意指使你 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, 真名…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 要和集結合 誰也別想阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 集 說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是被選中的一對適合者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將孕育新的種族 以血的交融
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行喲 集！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有生氣的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是拋開了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候你傷害了我吧 集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也不記得了嗎 忘記了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 要懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你只會讓人操心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯！ 傷勢如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開了要害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被結晶化的結晶救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.53,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(555,665)}cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恙神涯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等待這個時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和你還有真名對峙的這個瞬間！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偷拍下來的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和拍到虛空那時候一樣 都是雜訊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:03.87,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(503,665)}void
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個可以清楚的看到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是質點研究的試作篩檢程式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼讓我們通過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被從主會場趕出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一個小小的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 已經晚了 命運無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集 快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶇 緊急彈出！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯 我還能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋的契約 現在 在此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集 想起來吧 那天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該記得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落的耶誕節
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2029年12月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被你的新母親櫻滿春夏 帶到了東京
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後12月24日 我把你叫到六本木的教會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了聊關於你並不知道的真名的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那天來的人 並不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶誕節快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特萊登是我的騎士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今後也請守護我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準那顆星星 開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特萊登 我曾經喜歡著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特萊登？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特萊登？怎麼了 特萊登？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來抽吧 集
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我們的遺傳基因 建造一個新的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來做有趣的事吧 集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這 怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕 姐姐也很害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 我就會變得不再是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是真名因為暴走的力量把自己也給毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那時候真名在向我們求救
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們卻沒法回應她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 涯這麼說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 要變強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我靠忘記這一切來保護自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集 現在你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有不得不完成的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要奪回真名的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要靠自己的力量讓被他們強行喚醒的真名再一次沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她的惡意 用虛空的力量埋葬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:03.89,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(672,665)}void
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開了記憶的鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入了新的王的領域嗎 櫻滿集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有時間了 快把我的心抽出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把抽出來的虛空交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:22.10,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(726,665)}void
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你應該能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要鬆開手就這麼抽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是涯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集 跑起來 你掩護我跑向真名那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集 你在呼喚誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把虛空強制召喚出來的虛空？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:20.60,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,665)}void                          void
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠抽取人心的槍嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下吧 修一郎 你已經失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我和真名一起刺穿吧 集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我已經沒救了 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集 你現在眼中的我是什麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候的你 有決斷力 勇敢 強大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要成為那樣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯 你說什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候都能變成和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我成為了你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後的就靠你自己幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特萊登？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名 終於見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯！ 涯！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯一定很滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說 謝謝





